* Training 1
React and webpack

- Install Dependencies
npm install --save-dev babel babel-core babel-loader babel-preset-es2015 babel-preset-react

- Loaders
npm install --save-dev stlye-loader css-loader file-loader node-sass sass-loader csv-loader xml-loader

- Plugin
npm install --save-dev extract-text-webpack-plugin html-webpack-plugin

- webpack
- Install webpack related
npm install --save webpack webpack-dev-server webpack-merge

1. webpack.config.js

2. config/
helpers.js
webpack.common.js
webpack.dev.js
webpack.prod.js
webpack.stg.js

- webpack version 2

src/index.jsx
src/index.jsx

- HomePage
pages/HomePage.jsx


- Compile

- Start server

